00:27:53,932 --> 00:27:56,474
but it wasn't very cinematic or interesting.

412
00:27:56,474 --> 00:27:58,896
So we would add another layer on top of that

413
00:27:58,896 --> 00:28:01,038
just to kind of make it feel bigger

414
00:28:01,038 --> 00:28:03,139
and more impactful as you swung it.

