00:29:55,173 --> 00:30:03,479
And then we layered on top of those our existing generic bucket of sounds that we use for material impacts essentially.

436
00:30:04,820 --> 00:30:07,143
So yeah, that's what we did for those.

437
00:30:07,143 --> 00:30:10,145
And this next slide will show off some of the gameplay

438
00:30:10,145 --> 00:30:12,768
utilizing the systems mentioned previously

439
00:30:12,768 --> 00:30:15,850
with just the one-handed axe weapon, essentially.

440
00:30:45,957 --> 00:30:50,619
Those skeletons are fun to kill.

441
00:30:50,619 --> 00:30:52,399
So spells, these are actually my favorite.

442
00:30:52,399 --> 00:30:53,180
I like them a ton.

443
00:30:53,180 --> 00:30:55,580
I don't really miss grenades at all,

444
00:30:55,580 --> 00:30:57,301
and I think if you play Wonderlands,

445
00:30:57,301 --> 00:30:59,042
you'll probably feel the same way.

446
00:30:59,042 --> 00:31:01,382
But the spells are also extremely modular,

447
00:31:01,382 --> 00:31:03,243
but their core component can be kind of broken down

448
00:31:03,243 --> 00:31:06,664
into a few main high-level categories.

449
00:31:06,664 --> 00:31:08,985
That would be casting, projectiles, and spell mods.

450
00:31:08,985 --> 00:31:11,866
And casting is very varied.

451
00:31:11,866 --> 00:31:13,666
This is all the different types of casting

452
00:31:13,666 --> 00:31:14,227
that can occur.

453
00:31:16,047 --> 00:31:21,296
So without going into too much detail, absent from this list are a bunch of the uniques,

454
00:31:21,296 --> 00:31:25,443
which are like the legendaries and stuff like that. But I don't want to spoil those.

455
00:31:28,806 --> 00:31:31,867
So there are different types of buildups, loops, and casts

456
00:31:31,867 --> 00:31:32,767
that can be performed.

457
00:31:32,767 --> 00:31:35,569
For example, you may have a spell

458
00:31:35,569 --> 00:31:39,010
that casts a magical elemental missile via a wand,

459
00:31:39,010 --> 00:31:41,111
or you may see a spell that casts fireballs

460
00:31:41,111 --> 00:31:43,071
from the player's hands.

