00:31:43,071 --> 00:31:46,153
Some types of spells can instantly cast,

462
00:31:46,153 --> 00:31:48,133
while some can just cast.

463
00:31:48,594 --> 00:31:52,997
like be held down and then let go and then you can cast it that way.

464
00:31:52,997 --> 00:31:56,500
The casting times can also change based on the timing of the

