00:32:02,926 --> 00:32:09,211
All these variables come together in the system to create a lot of variety and interesting dynamics

467
00:32:09,211 --> 00:32:12,754
that can change basically the moment to moment gameplay

468
00:32:12,754 --> 00:32:13,935
and play styles up quite a lot.

